<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩ - <span class="c2">(١٠٥٥)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3689">أَبُو سَعِيدٍ الْأَشَجُّ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1611">أَبُو أُسَامَةَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشَ </a>ذَكَرَ عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4642">عُمَارَةَ بْنِ الْقَعْقَاعِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> كَفَافًا .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>